Scientific and research note:
FanoSeq is an exploratory feature-engineering framework based on sequence-derived descriptors, octonion algebra, and Fano-plane-inspired representations. The public availability of this repository does not grant permission to reproduce, reuse, repackage, or publish the framework or its implementation without written permission.

